OL,3,CDoctor admits removing two patients
OL,4,Covaries without consent
OL,6,FA doctor who worked in Guernsey for
OL,7,Fthree years has admitted to removing
OL,8,Fthe ovaries of two patients at the
OL,9,FPrincess Elizabeth Hospital without
OL,10,Ftheir consent.
OL,12,F'Patient C' received the surgery on 4
OL,13,FSeptember 2018 with 'Patient D'
OL,14,Fgetting the operation on 29 November
OL,15,Fof the same year.
