OL,3,CDoctor admits removing two patients
OL,4,Covaries without consent
OL,6,FThe revelations came at a tribunal in
OL,7,FManchester looking into whether
OL,8,Fobstetrician and gynaecologist Ali
OL,9,FShokouh-Amiri is fit to practice in a
OL,10,Fcase brought by the General Medical
OL,11,FCouncil.
OL,13,FHe is accused of failing to provide
OL,14,Fgood clinical care to six patients in
OL,15,FGuernsey during 2017 and 2018.
OL,17,FShokouh-Amiri admitted a number of
OL,18,Ffailings relating to inappropriate
OL,19,Fbehaviour, including not having a
OL,20,Fchaperone present when undertaking
OL,21,Fintimate examinations.
