OL,3,CDoctor admits removing two patients
OL,4,Covaries without consent
OL,6,FThe charge list includes 70 other
OL,7,Fallegations relating to sexually
OL,8,Fmotivated conduct towards patients
OL,9,Fwhich have yet to be determined.
OL,11,FThe Medical Specialist Group has
OL,12,Fpreviously confirmed that Shokouh-
OL,13,FAmiri worked for them from 31 October
OL,14,F2016 to 31 August 2019 when he left
OL,15,Fthe partnership.
OL,17,FHe has not seen patients in Guernsey
OL,18,Fsince January 2019.
