OL,6,FThe case is expected to last until 14
OL,7,FFebruary and is being heard by the
OL,8,FMedical Practitioners Tribunal
OL,9,FService, an independent body separate
OL,10,Ffrom the General Medical Council.
OL,12,FIt has the power to stop a doctor from
OL,13,Fworking in the UK if it thinks they
OL,14,Fare unfit to practice.
